OL,5, P&O Ferries has been forced to reverse 
OL,6, an attempt to pay its new, cheaper     
OL,7, seafarers less money.                  
OL,9,FIt comes after the RMT Union received  
OL,10,Freports of agency workers at Dover     
OL,11,Fbeing asked to sign contracts replacing
OL,12,Ftheir old ones with reduced payment.   
OL,14,FThe union reported P&O Ferries to the  
OL,15,FMaritime and Coastguard Agency, which  
OL,16,Fensured the new workers retained their 
OL,17,Foriginal wages.                        
OL,19,FThe company has been asked for comment 
OL,20,Fbut has so far not responded.          
